      h3 Currently working on
      p
        | <a href="http://www.nodelove.com/" target="_blank">Node Love</a> is a nifty little MongoDB driven Node.js
        | starter template. <a href="http://camelize.com/" target="_blank">Camelize Me</a> is an online tool that
        | converts arbitrary text to camel case. I also occasionally contribute to various open source projects.

      h3.second Currently learning
      p
        | My favorite thing at the moment is implementing <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Representational_state_transfer" target="_blank">RESTful</a> APIs with <a href="http://sailsjs.org/" target="_blank">Sails.js</a>,
        | a realtime MVC Framework for <a href="http://nodejs.org/" target="_blank">Node.js</a>. I am eagerly tinkering with
        | <a href="http://angularjs.org/" target="_blank">AngularJS</a> for fast, maintainable
        | <a class="_blank" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Single-page_application">single page applications</a>. I am also learning
        | cool <a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/html5-author/history.html#history" target="_blank">HTML5 browser history manipulation</a>
        | magic, the inner workings of the <a href="http://www.archlinux.org/" target="_blank">Arch Linux</a> distro,
        | <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scalability" target="_blank">application scalability</a>, the art of
        | <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zen" target="_blank">Zen</a>, and how to use
        | <a href="http://www.omnigroup.com/products/omnifocus/" target="_blank">Omnifocus</a> to effectively manage my time.

      h3.second Client projects
      p I am in the process of migrating my personal portfolio to this page. Until then, you can see examples of my work on <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/wyoumans?tab=repositories">my Github profile</a>
